Postmaster Lin has received a standing commission from Kowloon's transit authority for a complete route survey of the Great Northern Forest. The forest spans a vast area and its full extent has never been comprehensively documented in the city's navigation archive. Traverse every accessible trail, clearing, and sector within the forest and return with a complete route record.
Your Great Northern Forest survey has been filed with Kowloon's transit authority archive. Postmaster Lin has marked the commission fulfilled and the completed route record has been incorporated into the regional navigation reference files used by the city's dispatch office.
